SUMMARY OF POSITION


Our client is one a manufacturer, producing most of the collection, essentially textile, in its several factories in Asia. All Research &Development, Sales & Marketing and logistics are managed from its head counter in Europa.
The Admin & Finance Director will be in charge of overseeing all financial, accounting, and administration aspects of the local production unit in Cambodia. The Admin & Finance Director is reporting directly to the Head Office in Europa.

MAIN DUTIES AND RESPONSIBILITIES


• Design and implement administrative and accounting organization;
• Ensure corporate policies are understood and followed by the facility;
• Ensures the company is in compliance with all internal and external regulations, policies and procedures and reports as appropriate to the relevant authorities and or internal departments;
• Provide operational monitoring of accounting and management control;
• Manage, coordinate and oversees the financial requirement of the facility;
• Establish and maintain a good working relationship with outside auditors, banks and other third parties as needed;
• Develop and monitor closely the Financial aspects of the Annual Operational Plan, forecasting needs and strategic planning;
• Measure Facilities performance, develops appropriate Financial and Operational performance metrics;
• Produce accurate monthly financial analysis and financial reporting.

Reporting
• Report directly to the Head Finance Department located in Europa.
• Under direct supervision of the Country President.

Job Requirement:
• Degree in Accounting and/or Finance and/or Professional Accounting Qualification;
• Minimum 5 to 10 years Admin & Finance management experience;
• Strong back-ground in general business acumen are a must;
• Financial and manufacturing systems experience, manufacturing accounting experience is a plus;
• Strong influence, interpersonal, communication, problem solving, follow-up and creative solution generation skills.
• Professional proficiency in English (French is a plus).

SALARY RANGE

$2000-$3000

